Striker! is an app for keeping track of your soccer game stats like score, goals for and against, as well as your own stats like goals and assists. If you are on different teams, for example a High School team and a Club team, you can view all of the totals or filter it down to a specific league, home games, only the games you won, along with many other options. If you are looking for a simple, easy to use app to keep track of your details, then Striker! is the perfect app for you!
